	<div class="posts">
	<a name="86601831">&nbsp;</a><br>
	<h1>Groupware and Collaboration</h1><h2>Wiki Wacky</h2>Hey, I should use that, or wacky wiki or ...<h3>Archipelago implementation</h3><a href="http://archipelago.phrasewise.com/faq">Archipelago FAQ</a>.&nbsp; Well, OK, it is toolcraft-heavy.&nbsp; Hmm, are my blogs this disconnected and context-dependent?&nbsp; Probably.&nbsp; Ponder later.<br>
