	<a href="http://creativecommons.org/press-releases/entry/3476">Creative Commons Unveils Machine-Readable Copyright Licenses</a>.&nbsp; Related to discovery, and reached from Archepelago.&nbsp; This fruit bears all the symptoms of a depth-first traversal, so bear with me.<br>
