	<div class="posts">
	<a name="86601202">&nbsp;</a><br>
	<h3>Really simple discovery</h3><a href="http://archipelago.phrasewise.com/stories/storyReader$1330">RFC: Really Simple Discoverability 1.0</a>.&nbsp; This seems like a way to make discovery of the requirements for editing a site discoverable so that people can use different editors and other mechanisms.&nbsp; I find this page rather opaque, probably because it carries a heavy toolcraft assumption that I am clueless about.&nbsp; Suggested by Gary Johnson on BA-UnRev-Talk, I will blog enough to figure out how to come back to this.<br>
	<span class="byline">posted by Dennis at <a href="#86601202">Friday, December 27, 2002</a></span></div>
