	<h3>The historical Kasparov vs. Deep Blue matches</h3><a href="http://www.research.ibm.com/deepblue/home/html/b.html">IBM Research | Deep Blue | Overview</a>.&nbsp; Information on the 1997 rematch won by Deep Blue, 3-1/2 to 2-1/2 over Gary Kasparov.  There are also links to the previous match, won by Kasparov 4-2 and in which Deep Blue recorded the first won game against a World Champion in match play.<br>
	<span class="byline">posted by Dennis at <a href="#86404835">Sunday, December 22, 2002</a></span></div>
<br>
